<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạnṭq ʿly̱ lsạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹nṭq ʿly̱ lsạny wkn ynbwʿ klạmy
 ạrfʿ nḥwk ʿywny wkn mṣdr slạmy
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹mlạny bạlmḥbh wsr ạ̉nt ạmạmy
 2- hyỷny bạlqdạsh hymn ʿly̱ kyạny
 whbny msḥh mnk wbạrk fy ạ̹ymạny
 3- syṭr ʿly̱ ạ̉fkạry wkn nwrạaⁿ lạ̉ḥlạmy
 wạ̹smḥ lsẖhd ṣwtk ysry fy ạdẖạny
 4- ltḥyạ ạ̉nt fyạ wlạ ạ̉nạ ạ̉nạ ly
 ḥty̱ yrạk ạlkl fyạ wfy ạʿmạly
 5- wạsmḥ lrwḥk ạlqdws yạ̉ty wymlạ̉ny
 wlyfḍ fy rwḥk ạnt ạldẖy ạ̹sẖtrạny</lyrics>
